sub_title: Senior Project and Key Account Manager / Creative & Strategic Content Producer with Texts Writing and Photos and Films Producing
summary:
Creative Content Producer based between Amsterdam and Paris, with extensive expertise in marketing and communications tools, prints and digital. Skilled in making the bridge between business-driven missions and creative production, within multi-cultural and multi-lingual environments. Fluent in English and French, with basic working knowledge in Dutch, Japanese and Italian. 

www.littlebigpictures.eu
